OL,5, Holiday companies have urged the prime 
OL,6, minister to give extra powers to the   
OL,7, aviation watchdog to directly fine     
OL,8, airlines for service failures.         
OL,10,FIn a joint letter along with consumer  
OL,11,Forganisation Which?, they called for   
OL,12,Fstronger enforcement action if airlines
OL,13,Ffail to uphold consumer rights around  
OL,14,Frefunds and cancellations.             
OL,16,FIt claims thousands of passengers have 
OL,17,Fbeen subjected to "unfair treatment".  
OL,19,FThe industry body for airlines said    
OL,20,Faviation was already highly regulated. 
